Installation Instructions
-------------------------


Dependencies
-----------------------

qt4 (must have qt version 4.4 or greater)
cmake (this is the build system used, verion 2.6 or greater)
boost C++ libraries 
boost-filesystem
dime (for DXF file output, must be BSD version of dime available here https://bitbucket.org/Coin3D/dime
	  ubuntu currently packages the GPL version of dime)


Build and run instructions
----------------------------

1. run cmake ./
2. run make
3. execute psketcher in the src/Interface directory


Example build and run process
------------------------------------

cmake .
make
./src/Interface/psketcher



